= Take Control

Whether or not we are preparing for ascension, the Cabal is always trying to tighten its grasp on mortal souls. Who should we focus our efforts on?

- @workers: The needful masses ruled by Desire, our preferred prey.
- @new_middle: The cold-eyed servitors and spiteful enforcers of Cruelty.
- @old_middle: The Pride-wracked tyrants and those who would take their place.
- @rural: Chaos emissaries and temporal exiles, who had felt forgotten by us in the unwritten futures.
- @unemployed: The Hollow ones, whose hearts and minds have been consumed.
- @catholics: Clockwork-minded zealots of the First Machine, who typically support the Neo-Templars.
- @root: We either don't want to or cannot control any additional souls right now.
- @easy_discard

@workers
subtitle: -1 mana
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough mana.
on-arrival: workers_spd += 6*(1-dissent); workers_spd -= 2 if unemployed >= 15; workers_spd -= 2 if unemployed >= 25; workers_spd += 6*(1-dissent) if wtb_adopted = 1; resources -= 1; workers_spd += 3*(1-dissent) if nationalization_progress >= 1;

In a universe full of scarcity and loss, desire is the universal language that we have learned to speak perfectly. [? if unemployed >= 15: The icy winds from the dying sun quench the flames of yearning and impede our efforts. ?][? if wtb_adopted = 1 : Like moths to a furnace, the needful masses are drawn to the radiance of our False Star. ?]

@new_middle
subtitle: -1 mana
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough mana.
on-arrival: new_middle_spd += 6*(1-dissent); new_middle_spd -= 4 if socialism <= 49 and peoples_party == 0; resources -= 1; peoples_party_support += 1;

In our hands, pain and death become chains to bind the cruel to our Will. [? if socialism <= 49 and peoples_party == 0: Their mental corrosion makes them inflexible and barely responsive to our commands. ?] [? if peoples_party > 0: With the Emeraldine Tablets broken, the barbed hooks of our bloodshed and butchery snare far more cruel hearts than before. ?]

@old_middle
subtitle: -1 mana
