The ambitious and proud are few in number, yet each is a singular prize. [? if nationalism >= 51 and peoples_party == 0: The pervasive undercurrent of dread makes them paranoid and wary of our schemes. ?] [? if peoples_party > 0: With the Emeraldine Tablets broken, we can make Faustian bargains with them, trading power for souls. ?]

@rural
subtitle: -1 mana
