We have done what we could to strengthen our grip on the time-lost. [? if peoples_party == 0: Our histories do not entirely overlap, and they do not bow to us. ?][? if peoples_party > 0: With the Emeraldine Tablets broken, we are free to engage in once-forbidden rites that grant us greater control than before. ?][? if rural_policy >= 2 : Our chronal edicts have brought them closer to our timeline. ?]

