The Hollow, bereft of urge and Will as they are, are puppets for anyone who deigns to pull their strings. [? if welfare < 0: Yet given our karmic resonance with the rites that hollowed them out in the first place, there is a risk that we may end up being the ones puppeted. Strings run both ways, after all. ?][? if wtb_adopted = 1 : The radiance of the False Star enthralls the hollow. ?]

